    "createdBy": "admin",
    "updatedBy": "admin",
    "tags": ["design-patterns", "general-design-patterns", "advanced"],
    "explanation": "In Observer, observers subscribe directly to the observable, creating tight coupling. In Pub/Sub, a mediator (event bus) manages communication, decoupling publishers and subscribers.",
    "points": 10,
    "sampleAnswers": [
      "In Observer, observers subscribe directly to the observable, creating tight coupling.",
